#### to the `census.gov/popclock` website, scroll to the bottom to the box labeled <b>Most Populous</b> and select <b>States</b>.
####
#### The reason that <b>States</b> is selected, in contrast to Counties or Cities is due to the geographic range difference that is present when
#### selecting <b>States</b> is greater than when selecting Counties or Cities. By selecting <b>States</b> we encompass a greater geographic
